<item>
            <title>[SPARK-21929] Support `ALTER TABLE table_name ADD COLUMNS(..)` for ORC data source</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-21929</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-19261&quot; title=&quot;Support `ALTER TABLE table_name ADD COLUMNS(..)` statement&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SPARK-19261&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SPARK-19261&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; implemented `ADD COLUMNS` at Spark 2.2, but ORC data source is not supported due to its limit.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
scala&amp;gt; sql(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;CREATE TABLE tab (c1 &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;, c2 &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;, c3 &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;) USING ORC PARTITIONED BY (c3)&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
scala&amp;gt; sql(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;ALTER TABLE tab ADD COLUMNS (c4 &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;)&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
org.apache.spark.sql.AnalysisException:
ALTER ADD COLUMNS does not support datasource table with type ORC.
You must drop and re-create the table &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; adding the &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; columns. Tables: `tab`;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
